KEYBINDINGS
===========

Mode Independent / Mode Change
------------------------------

`   = Switch to Movement Mode
l   = Look around
@   = Character Screen
i   = Inventory Screen (Not implemented)
g   = Game Info (Not implemented)
F1  = Help text (Not implemented)
F12 = Quit

Movement Mode
-------------

qwe 789
asd 456 = Movement
zxc 123

Arrow Keys = Move Camera
<  = Go up stairs
>  = Go down stairs

, = Pickup gold/items

Map Look Mode
-------------

qwe 789
asd 456 = Move reticle
zxc 123

Arrow Keys = Move Camera
